Problem set from chapter 3

4. 
--------------------------------- 
receive(A,a,B,b);
while (a>b) loop      <= (1)
    if (a>b) then
        a <= a - b;
        wait for 5 ns;
    else
        b <= b - a;
        wait for 5 ns;
    end if;
end loop;
end if;              <== (2)
send(C,a)            <== (3)
---------------------------------

(1) a=3 and b=8, this code will send back 3. Not the correct answer!
         suggest:  replace (a>b) wiht (a>0 and b>0)

(2) No coresponding 'if' 

(3) a not always holding the gcd
       suggest:  if (a=0) then
                     send(C,b);
                 else
                     send(C,a);


